  'jasa-pembuatan-website-wonosobo',
  'Jasa Pembuatan Website Profesional di Wonosobo',
  'Professional Web Development Services in Wonosobo',
  'Butuh jasa membuat web di Wonosobo? Bratamedia hadir dengan solusi website profesional untuk bisnis lokal, UMKM, dan toko online di Wonosobo dan Jawa Tengah.',
  'Looking for web development in Wonosobo? Bratamedia builds professional websites for local businesses, SMEs, and online stores across Wonosobo and Central Java.',
  '{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jasa Pembuatan Website Profesional di Wonosobo: Solusi Digital untuk Bisnis Lokal yang Ingin Berkembang"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wonosobo bukan sekadar kota transit menuju Dieng. Di balik kabut pegunungan dan hamparan kebun teh yang ikonik, ada ribuan pelaku usaha yang setiap hari berjuang membesarkan bisnisnya — dari pedagang di sekitar Alun-Alun Wonosobo, penginapan di kawasan wisata Dieng, hingga UMKM kuliner yang produknya sudah dikenal seantero Jawa Tengah."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Satu pertanyaan yang sering muncul: "},{"type":"text","text":"bagaimana caranya agar bisnis di Wonosobo bisa ditemukan lebih banyak orang, termasuk mereka yang mencari secara online?","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jawabannya dimulai dari sebuah website yang profesional."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia hadir di Wonosobo bukan sekadar sebagai penyedia jasa, melainkan sebagai mitra digital yang memahami kebutuhan bisnis lokal dari dalam."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mengapa Bisnis di Wonosobo Membutuhkan Website Sekarang?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perilaku konsumen berubah drastis dalam beberapa tahun terakhir. Ketika seseorang ingin mencari penginapan di Dieng, memesan katering untuk acara di Wonosobo, atau mencari kontraktor lokal, hal pertama yang mereka lakukan bukan menelepon kenalan — mereka membuka Google."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jika bisnis Anda tidak muncul di sana, calon pelanggan itu pergi ke kompetitor yang sudah punya website."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Beberapa fakta yang perlu Anda tahu:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Lebih dari 90% konsumen Indonesia melakukan riset online sebelum memutuskan untuk membeli atau menggunakan jasa."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bisnis dengan website profesional dinilai lebih kredibel dibandingkan yang hanya mengandalkan media sosial."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website bekerja 24 jam sehari, 7 hari seminggu — menerima pertanyaan, menampilkan produk, dan membangun kepercayaan bahkan saat toko Anda tutup."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Di Wonosobo yang ekosistem bisnisnya terus berkembang — dari sektor pariwisata, pertanian, kuliner, hingga jasa profesional — memiliki website bukan lagi kemewahan. Ini adalah kebutuhan dasar."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Apa yang Membuat Bratamedia Berbeda?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Banyak jasa pembuatan website yang menawarkan harga murah, tapi hasilnya mengecewakan — desain yang kaku, website lambat, atau tim yang tidak responsif setelah proyek selesai."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia bekerja dengan pendekatan yang berbeda."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tim yang Berpengalaman, Proses yang Terstruktur"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Setiap proyek kami dimulai dengan sesi konsultasi untuk memahami bisnis Anda: siapa target pelanggan Anda, apa yang ingin Anda capai, dan seperti apa identitas visual yang ingin Anda bangun. Baru setelah itu kami masuk ke tahap desain dan pengembangan."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kami tidak menjual template jadi yang dipoles ulang. Kami membangun website yang dirancang khusus sesuai kebutuhan bisnis Anda — dari alur navigasi, konten, hingga optimasi untuk mesin pencari (SEO) agar website Anda mudah ditemukan di Google."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hadir Secara Lokal, Berpikir Secara Digital"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia memiliki kantor di Wonosobo, tepatnya di Jl. Sabuk Alu RT 001/007, Wonosobo Timur, Kecamatan Wonosobo, Kabupaten Wonosobo, Jawa Tengah 56311. Ini bukan sekadar alamat — ini artinya tim kami bisa bertemu langsung dengan Anda, memahami konteks bisnis lokal Anda, dan memberikan dukungan yang tidak terputus setelah website diluncurkan."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kami juga memiliki kantor di Semarang, sehingga Anda mendapat kekuatan tim yang besar dengan kedekatan yang lokal."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Klien dari Berbagai Sektor"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia sudah dipercaya oleh klien dari berbagai sektor bisnis — dari usaha kuliner dan pariwisata, hingga perusahaan jasa dan pelaku e-commerce. Pengalaman lintas industri ini membuat kami memahami bahwa setiap bisnis punya kebutuhan yang unik, dan tidak ada satu solusi yang cocok untuk semua."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Layanan Website yang Kami Tawarkan"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bergantung pada kebutuhan bisnis Anda, kami menyediakan berbagai jenis website:"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website Company Profile"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ideal untuk bisnis yang ingin membangun kehadiran online yang profesional dan kredibel. Company profile website menampilkan informasi perusahaan, layanan, tim, dan cara menghubungi Anda — semua dalam satu halaman yang bersih dan mudah dinavigasi."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cocok untuk: agen properti, firma hukum, klinik, konsultan, dan bisnis jasa lainnya di Wonosobo."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website Toko Online (E-Commerce)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Untuk bisnis yang ingin menjual produk secara online — baik ke pelanggan Wonosobo maupun ke seluruh Indonesia. Kami membangun toko online yang dilengkapi dengan sistem manajemen produk, keranjang belanja, integrasi pembayaran, dan fitur pengiriman."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cocok untuk: UMKM produk lokal Wonosobo (keripik, mie ongklok, carica, kopi Dieng), butik fashion, dan toko retail yang ingin ekspansi digital."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website Landing Page"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Halaman tunggal yang dirancang untuk satu tujuan: mengkonversi pengunjung menjadi prospek atau pelanggan. Landing page efektif untuk kampanye promosi, peluncuran produk baru, atau penawaran jasa spesifik."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website Portal & Aplikasi Web"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Untuk kebutuhan yang lebih kompleks — sistem manajemen internal, portal pelanggan, atau aplikasi web berbasis data. Ini adalah ranah keahlian utama Bratamedia sebagai software house."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Proses Kerja Kami: Dari Konsep hingga Peluncuran"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kami percaya transparansi adalah fondasi kolaborasi yang baik. Inilah tahapan yang akan Anda jalani bersama tim Bratamedia:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Konsultasi Awal","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Kami mendengarkan kebutuhan Anda, memahami tujuan bisnis, dan mendiskusikan solusi yang paling tepat."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perencanaan & Wireframe","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Tim kami membuat kerangka struktur website sebelum masuk ke desain visual, sehingga alur dan konten sudah disepakati sejak awal."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Desain UI/UX","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Tampilan website dirancang dengan mempertimbangkan estetika, kenyamanan pengguna, dan identitas brand Anda."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pengembangan","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Tim developer kami membangun website menggunakan teknologi terkini — cepat, aman, dan mudah dikelola."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Uji Coba & Revisi","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Website diuji di berbagai perangkat dan browser sebelum diluncurkan. Anda mendapat kesempatan untuk memberikan masukan."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Peluncuran","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Website Anda resmi online dan siap menerima pengunjung."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dukungan Pasca-Peluncuran","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Kami tidak menghilang setelah proyek selesai. Tim kami tersedia untuk membantu jika ada pertanyaan atau kebutuhan pembaruan."}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pertanyaan yang Sering Diajukan"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Apakah saya harus mengerti teknologi untuk bisa pakai website dari Bratamedia?","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tidak perlu. Kami menjelaskan semuanya dalam bahasa yang mudah dipahami, dan kami merancang website dengan antarmuka pengelolaan yang sederhana sehingga Anda bisa memperbarui konten sendiri tanpa harus menjadi programmer."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Berapa lama proses pembuatan websitenya?","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tergantung kompleksitas proyek. Website company profile umumnya selesai dalam 2–4 minggu. Toko online atau aplikasi web bisa membutuhkan waktu lebih lama, dan kami akan menyampaikan estimasi yang realistis sejak awal."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Apakah website saya akan muncul di Google?","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Setiap website yang kami bangun sudah dioptimasi secara teknis untuk SEO — struktur URL yang bersih, kecepatan loading yang baik, meta tag yang tepat, dan desain yang mobile-friendly. Untuk hasil maksimal, kami juga menyediakan layanan SEO lanjutan secara terpisah."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bisnis Lokal Wonosobo yang Berkembang, Butuh Fondasi Digital yang Kuat"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wonosobo punya potensi besar. Sektor pariwisata di kawasan Dieng terus tumbuh, produk UMKM lokal semakin dikenal di pasar nasional, dan jumlah pelaku usaha muda yang ambisious terus bertambah. Semua potensi ini butuh satu hal yang sama: kehadiran digital yang kuat dan profesional."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website bukan sekadar halaman di internet. Ini adalah representasi bisnis Anda di dunia digital — tempat calon pelanggan menilai kredibilitas Anda sebelum mereka memutuskan untuk menghubungi Anda."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Untuk bisnis di luar Wonosobo, kami juga melayani klien di seluruh Jawa Tengah. Baca juga artikel kami tentang "},{"type":"text","text":"jasa pembuatan website di Semarang","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/blog/jasa-pembuatan-website-semarang","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":" dan "},{"type":"text","text":"jasa pembuatan website untuk seluruh Jawa Tengah","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/blog/jasa-pembuatan-website-jawa-tengah","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mulai Perjalanan Digital Anda Bersama Bratamedia"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jika Anda adalah pemilik bisnis di Wonosobo yang ingin memiliki website profesional, kami mengundang Anda untuk berdiskusi dengan tim kami — tanpa biaya, tanpa komitmen."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hubungi kami melalui:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"WhatsApp / Telepon","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": 085155030061"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Email","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": m.iqmal.riffai@gmail.com"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kantor Wonosobo","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Jl. Sabuk Alu RT 001/007, Wonosobo Timur, Kec. Wonosobo, Kabupaten Wonosobo, Jawa Tengah 56311"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Atau kunjungi "},{"type":"text","text":"halaman kontak kami","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/kontak","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":" dan ceritakan kebutuhan Anda. Tim kami akan merespons dalam waktu 1x24 jam."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bisnis Anda layak mendapat kehadiran digital yang terbaik. Mari wujudkan itu bersama."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"}]}'::jsonb,
  '{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Professional Website Development in Wonosobo: Digital Solutions for Local Businesses Ready to Grow"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wonosobo is more than a stopover on the way to the Dieng Plateau. Nestled in the highlands of Central Java, it is a city with a quietly thriving business ecosystem — from traders operating around the Wonosobo town square, guesthouses catering to Dieng tourists, to small businesses whose products have found customers across the province and beyond."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yet one challenge persists for many of these businesses: "},{"type":"text","text":"how do you get found by more customers, including the ones searching online?","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The answer starts with a professional website."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia Digital Solutions is based in Wonosobo — not just in spirit, but with a physical office and a team that understands the local market from the inside."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Wonosobo Businesses Need a Website Right Now"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Consumer behavior has shifted decisively. When someone wants to find a guesthouse near Dieng, order catering for an event in Wonosobo, or hire a local contractor, the first thing they do is not call a contact — they open Google."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"If your business is not there, that potential customer goes to a competitor who already has a website."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A few numbers worth keeping in mind:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Over 90% of Indonesian consumers research online before making a purchase or booking a service."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Businesses with professional websites are perceived as more credible than those relying solely on social media."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A website works around the clock — capturing inquiries, showcasing products, and building trust even when your physical location is closed."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"In Wonosobo, where sectors like tourism, agriculture, food and beverage, and professional services continue to expand, having a website is no longer optional. It is a business fundamental."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What Makes Bratamedia Different?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Many web development providers compete on price alone — and the results often show it: rigid designs, slow-loading pages, and support that vanishes once the project is handed over."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia works differently."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"An Experienced Team, a Structured Process"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Every project begins with a consultation to understand your business: who your customers are, what you want to achieve, and what kind of brand experience you want to create. Only then do we move into design and development."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"We do not resell off-the-shelf templates with a fresh coat of paint. We build websites tailored to your business — from the navigation structure and content architecture, to search engine optimization (SEO) that helps your site rank on Google for the searches that matter to you."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Locally Present, Digitally Minded"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia has an office in Wonosobo at Jl. Sabuk Alu RT 001/007, Wonosobo Timur, Kecamatan Wonosobo, Kabupaten Wonosobo, Central Java 56311. That is not just an address — it means our team can meet you in person, understand the local business context firsthand, and provide support that does not end at go-live."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"We also operate out of Semarang, giving you the backing of a full-scale software house with the accessibility of a local partner."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Clients Across Industries"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia has served clients in hospitality, food and beverage, professional services, e-commerce, and more. This cross-sector experience means we understand that every business has unique needs — and that there is no single template for success."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website Services We Offer"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Depending on your business goals, we build several types of websites:"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Company Profile Website"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The right choice for businesses that want a credible, professional online presence. A company profile site presents your organization, services, team, and contact information in a clean, easy-to-navigate format."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ideal for: property agencies, legal firms, clinics, consultants, and service businesses in Wonosobo."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"E-Commerce Website"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"For businesses that want to sell online — to customers in Wonosobo and across Indonesia. We build online stores complete with product management systems, shopping carts, payment gateway integration, and shipping features."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ideal for: local Wonosobo product businesses (snacks, mie ongklok, carica fruit preserves, Dieng coffee), fashion boutiques, and retail shops looking to expand digitally."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Landing Page"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A single-purpose page designed to convert visitors into leads or customers. Landing pages are effective for promotional campaigns, product launches, or specific service offerings."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Web Portals & Web Applications"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"For more complex requirements — internal management systems, customer portals, or data-driven web applications. This is the core specialization of Bratamedia as a software house."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Our Process: From Concept to Launch"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"We believe transparency is the foundation of a good working relationship. Here is what working with Bratamedia looks like:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Initial Consultation","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — We listen to your needs, understand your business goals, and discuss the best solution for your situation."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Planning & Wireframe","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Our team creates a structural outline of your website before moving to visual design, so the flow and content are agreed upon from the start."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"UI/UX Design","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — The website''s appearance is crafted with aesthetics, usability, and your brand identity in mind."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Development","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Our developers build the website using modern technology — fast, secure, and easy to manage."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Testing & Revision","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — The website is tested across devices and browsers before launch. You have the opportunity to provide feedback and request revisions."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Launch","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Your website goes live and is ready to receive visitors."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Post-Launch Support","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — We do not disappear after delivery. Our team remains available for questions, updates, and ongoing support."}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Common Questions"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Do I need to understand technology to work with Bratamedia?","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Not at all. We communicate in plain language throughout the project, and we build websites with simple, intuitive content management interfaces so you can update your own content without needing a developer."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How long does it take to build a website?","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"It depends on the scope. A company profile website typically takes 2–4 weeks. An e-commerce site or web application may take longer, and we will give you a realistic timeline from the outset."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Will my website appear on Google?","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Every website we build is technically optimized for SEO — clean URL structures, good loading speeds, proper meta tags, and mobile-friendly design. For more advanced results, we also offer dedicated SEO services."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A Growing Local Economy Needs a Strong Digital Foundation"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wonosobo has real potential. Tourism around the Dieng Plateau continues to grow, locally made products are gaining recognition in national markets, and the number of ambitious young entrepreneurs in the city is steadily rising. All of this potential has one thing in common: it needs a strong, professional digital presence to reach its full scale."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A website is not just a page on the internet. It is the representation of your business in the digital world — the place where prospective customers form their first impression before they decide to reach out."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"For businesses outside Wonosobo, we also serve clients across Central Java. Read our articles on "},{"type":"text","text":"website development services in Semarang","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/blog/jasa-pembuatan-website-semarang","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","text":"website development services across Central Java","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/blog/jasa-pembuatan-website-jawa-tengah","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Start Your Digital Journey with Bratamedia"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"If you are a business owner in Wonosobo ready to build a professional website, we invite you to have a conversation with our team — at no cost, with no obligation."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Reach us through:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"WhatsApp / Phone","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": +62 851-5503-0061"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Email","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": m.iqmal.riffai@gmail.com"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wonosobo Office","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Jl. Sabuk Alu RT 001/007, Wonosobo Timur, Kec. Wonosobo, Kabupaten Wonosobo, Central Java 56311"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Or visit our "},{"type":"text","text":"contact page","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/kontak","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":" and tell us about your project. Our team responds within 24 hours."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Your business deserves a digital presence that works as hard as you do. Let''s build it together."}]}]}'::jsonb,
