  'Web Development Services in Central Java | Bratamedia',
  'Jasa membuat web Jawa Tengah melayani Solo, Semarang, Purwokerto, Kudus, dan seluruh Jateng. Bratamedia punya kantor di Semarang dan Wonosobo.',
  'Professional web development across Central Java — Solo, Semarang, Purwokerto, Kudus, and beyond. Bratamedia has offices in Semarang and Wonosobo.',
  '{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jasa Pembuatan Website Jawa Tengah: Melayani Solo, Semarang, Purwokerto, dan Seluruh Wilayah Jateng"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jawa Tengah adalah provinsi dengan karakter bisnis yang luar biasa beragam. Dalam satu provinsi yang sama, Anda bisa menemukan industri batik berusia ratusan tahun di Solo dan Pekalongan, pusat furnitur kayu dunia di Jepara, kawasan industri besar di Semarang, UMKM rokok dan makanan olahan di Kudus, potensi wisata kelas dunia di Borobudur dan Dieng, hingga kota-kota berkembang seperti Purwokerto, Tegal, Magelang, dan Cilacap yang terus bergeliat."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Semua keberagaman ini punya satu kebutuhan yang sama: "},{"type":"text","text":"kehadiran digital yang profesional untuk bersaing di era sekarang.","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia Digital Solutions hadir sebagai mitra pembuatan website yang memahami peta bisnis Jawa Tengah — bukan dari jauh, melainkan dari dalam. Kami memiliki kantor di "},{"type":"text","text":"Semarang","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" dan "},{"type":"text","text":"Wonosobo","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":", dua titik strategis yang memungkinkan kami melayani klien dari ujung barat hingga ujung timur provinsi ini."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mengapa Bisnis di Jawa Tengah Perlu Website Profesional Sekarang?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Persaingan bisnis di Jawa Tengah semakin ketat, dan medan pertempurannya sudah bergeser ke dunia digital. Calon pelanggan — baik dari dalam provinsi maupun dari luar daerah — hampir selalu memulai perjalanan pembelian mereka dengan pencarian di Google."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pengusaha batik di Laweyan, Solo, yang ingin menjangkau pembeli dari Jakarta? Mereka butuh website. Pengrajin furnitur di Jepara yang ingin ekspor ke luar negeri? Mereka butuh website. Pengusaha kuliner di Purwokerto yang ingin buka cabang franchise? Mereka butuh website. Hotel butik di kawasan wisata Borobudur, Magelang, yang ingin lepas dari ketergantungan pada OTA (Online Travel Agency)? Mereka pasti butuh website."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website bukan lagi sekadar \"kartu nama digital.\" Ia adalah saluran penjualan, alat membangun kepercayaan, dan fondasi dari seluruh strategi pemasaran digital."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia: Dua Kantor, Satu Komitmen untuk Seluruh Jawa Tengah"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Posisi geografis kami bukan kebetulan. Kantor "},{"type":"text","text":"Semarang","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" kami di Jl. Tanjungsari I No.18, Sumurboto, Kec. Banyumanik, Kota Semarang — ibukota provinsi dan pusat bisnis utama Jawa Tengah — memungkinkan kami melayani klien dari kawasan Semarang Raya, Kendal, Demak, dan kota-kota di sepanjang jalur pantura."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sementara kantor "},{"type":"text","text":"Wonosobo","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" kami di Jl. Sabuk Alu RT 001/007, Wonosobo Timur, Kecamatan Wonosobo — tepat di jantung wilayah Jawa Tengah bagian tengah — menjadi jembatan layanan untuk klien dari Purwokerto, Banjarnegara, Kebumen, Magelang, hingga Temanggung."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dua titik layanan ini bukan hanya soal kedekatan fisik. Ini soal pemahaman konteks: kami mengenal ekosistem bisnis lokal, kami tahu tantangan yang dihadapi pelaku usaha di masing-masing daerah, dan kami bisa bertemu langsung dengan klien tanpa harus bergantung sepenuhnya pada komunikasi digital."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jawa Tengah dan Kekayaan Ekosistem Bisnisnya"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Untuk memahami mengapa layanan "},{"type":"text","text":"jasa website Jawa Tengah","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" yang kontekstual sangat penting, perlu kita lihat betapa kayanya ekosistem bisnis di provinsi ini."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Solo dan Pekalongan: Ibu Kota Batik Indonesia"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Solo (Surakarta) dan Pekalongan adalah dua kota yang menjadi jantung industri batik nasional. Ratusan produsen batik, baik skala rumahan maupun pabrik besar, beroperasi di kedua kota ini. Pasar mereka sudah melampaui batas provinsi, bahkan batas negara."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Namun banyak pengusaha batik di sini masih mengandalkan penjualan melalui pasar fisik atau media sosial yang tidak terstruktur. Website toko online yang menampilkan katalog batik secara profesional, lengkap dengan fitur filter motif, ukuran, dan pilihan pengiriman ke seluruh dunia, bisa menjadi game-changer bagi bisnis mereka."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jepara: Furnitur untuk Dunia"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jepara adalah kota furnitur terbesar di Asia Tenggara. Ribuan workshop dan showroom furnitur berjajar di sini, dengan pasar ekspor yang mencakup Eropa, Amerika, dan Timur Tengah. Untuk skala bisnis seperti ini, website bukan pilihan — ini keharusan."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website yang menampilkan katalog produk dalam bahasa Inggris, dilengkapi sistem permintaan penawaran (request for quote), dan dioptimasi untuk pencarian internasional adalah aset bisnis yang nilainya jauh melampaui biaya pembuatannya."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kudus: UMKM dan Industri yang Dinamis"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kudus dikenal sebagai kota kretek dan industri makanan olahan. Di sini, ratusan UMKM beroperasi di sektor makanan, minuman, dan kerajinan. Banyak produk Kudus yang sudah dikenal secara nasional, tapi belum memiliki saluran penjualan digital yang terorganisir."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dengan website yang tepat, produk dari Kudus bisa menjangkau distributor baru, pelanggan ritel dari luar daerah, dan bahkan pembeli luar negeri yang mencari produk Indonesian artisanal."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Purwokerto dan Banyumas: Pusat Pertumbuhan Baru"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Purwokerto tumbuh cepat sebagai pusat pendidikan dan bisnis di Jawa Tengah bagian barat. Kehadiran Universitas Jenderal Soedirman (Unsoed) dan beberapa kampus besar lainnya menciptakan ekosistem bisnis yang dinamis: startup lokal, usaha kuliner mahasiswa yang ingin berkembang, lembaga kursus dan pelatihan, hingga properti dan kos-kosan."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Semua segmen ini butuh website — dari landing page sederhana hingga sistem manajemen yang lebih kompleks."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tegal, Brebes, Cilacap: Pantura dan Pesisir Selatan"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tegal dikenal dengan industri otomotif dan logam, serta kuliner ikoniknya. Brebes terkenal sebagai penghasil bawang merah terbesar Indonesia. Cilacap adalah kota industri penting dengan pelabuhan yang aktif."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Di kota-kota pesisir ini, transformasi digital bisnis masih dalam tahap awal — artinya potensi pertumbuhan bagi bisnis yang lebih dulu hadir secara online sangat besar."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Magelang dan Borobudur: Destinasi Wisata Kelas Dunia"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Candi Borobudur di Magelang adalah destinasi wisata yang menarik jutaan pengunjung setiap tahun, termasuk wisatawan mancanegara. Bisnis di sekitar kawasan ini — hotel, restoran, operator tur, toko suvenir, pengrajin lokal — memiliki peluang besar untuk menjangkau tamu internasional yang sudah terbiasa melakukan riset dan pemesanan secara online."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website multibahasa dengan sistem reservasi yang terintegrasi bisa menjadi pembeda yang signifikan bagi bisnis pariwisata di Magelang dan sekitarnya."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Layanan Website yang Kami Tawarkan untuk Bisnis Jawa Tengah"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia bukan hanya membangun website — kami membangun solusi digital yang sesuai dengan konteks dan tujuan bisnis spesifik Anda."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website Company Profile"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Presentasi bisnis yang profesional dan terpercaya. Ideal untuk perusahaan di Semarang, Solo, atau kota manapun di Jawa Tengah yang ingin membangun kehadiran online yang berbobot — firm hukum, konsultan, agensi, distributor, kontraktor, dan sejenisnya."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website Toko Online (E-Commerce)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dari pedagang batik di Solo hingga pengrajin furnitur di Jepara, e-commerce adalah kanal penjualan yang tidak bisa diabaikan. Kami membangun toko online yang fungsional, mudah dikelola, dan dioptimasi untuk konversi."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Landing Page"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Satu halaman, satu tujuan: mengubah pengunjung menjadi prospek. Efektif untuk kampanye promosi, peluncuran produk baru, atau penawaran jasa spesifik. Cocok untuk bisnis yang baru memulai kehadiran digital."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website Portal dan Aplikasi Web"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Untuk kebutuhan yang lebih kompleks: sistem manajemen agen properti, portal pelanggan, sistem reservasi hotel, atau platform bisnis lainnya. Ini adalah inti keahlian Bratamedia sebagai software house."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Proses Kerja Kami: Dari Konsultasi hingga Go-Live"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cara kami bekerja selalu dimulai dari mendengarkan. Kami tidak datang dengan template yang sudah jadi dan memaksanya cocok dengan bisnis Anda. Kami memulai dari nol bersama Anda."}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Konsultasi & Analisis Kebutuhan","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Kami memahami bisnis Anda, target pelanggan, dan tujuan yang ingin dicapai melalui website."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perencanaan & Wireframe","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Struktur website dirancang sebelum masuk ke visual, sehingga semua pihak sepakat sejak awal."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Desain UI/UX","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Tampilan yang mencerminkan identitas brand Anda, dirancang untuk kenyamanan pengguna di desktop dan mobile."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pengembangan","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Dibangun dengan teknologi terkini: cepat, aman, mudah dikelola."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Uji Coba & Revisi","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Diuji lintas perangkat dan browser. Anda punya kesempatan penuh untuk memberikan masukan."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Peluncuran","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Website resmi online, siap menerima pengunjung dan menghasilkan prospek."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dukungan Pasca-Peluncuran","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Kami tetap ada setelah proyek selesai, siap membantu untuk pembaruan, pertanyaan, atau pengembangan lanjutan."}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jangkauan Lebih Luas: Bratamedia Juga Melayani Seluruh Indonesia"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Meskipun kami berakar di Jawa Tengah, jangkauan layanan Bratamedia tidak terbatas pada provinsi ini. Kami sudah melayani klien dari berbagai kota di Indonesia, dan proyek digital tidak mengenal batas geografis."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Untuk bisnis di Wonosobo, baca artikel kami tentang "},{"type":"text","text":"jasa pembuatan website di Wonosobo","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/blog/jasa-pembuatan-website-wonosobo","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":". Jika Anda di Semarang, kami juga punya panduan lengkap di artikel "},{"type":"text","text":"jasa pembuatan website di Semarang","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/blog/jasa-pembuatan-website-semarang","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":". Dan jika Anda mencari mitra untuk proyek berskala nasional, pelajari lebih lanjut di artikel "},{"type":"text","text":"jasa pembuatan website Indonesia","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/blog/jasa-pembuatan-website-indonesia","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Atau kunjungi "},{"type":"text","text":"halaman layanan kami","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/layanan","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":" untuk melihat gambaran lengkap solusi digital yang kami tawarkan."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mulai Diskusi Hari Ini"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jika Anda adalah pemilik bisnis di Solo, Semarang, Purwokerto, Kudus, Pekalongan, Jepara, Magelang, Tegal, Cilacap, Wonosobo — atau kota manapun di Jawa Tengah — dan Anda ingin memiliki website yang benar-benar bekerja untuk bisnis Anda, tim Bratamedia siap berdiskusi."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tidak perlu menyiapkan brief yang sempurna. Cukup ceritakan bisnis Anda dan apa yang ingin Anda capai. Kami akan membimbing prosesnya dari sana."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hubungi kami melalui:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"WhatsApp / Telepon","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": 085155030061"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Email","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": m.iqmal.riffai@gmail.com"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kantor Semarang","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Jl. Tanjungsari I No.18, Sumurboto, Kec. Banyumanik, Kota Semarang, Jawa Tengah 50269"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kantor Wonosobo","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Jl. Sabuk Alu RT 001/007, Wonosobo Timur, Kec. Wonosobo, Kabupaten Wonosobo, Jawa Tengah 56311"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Atau kunjungi "},{"type":"text","text":"halaman kontak kami","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/kontak","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":" dan ceritakan kebutuhan Anda. Tim kami merespons dalam 1x24 jam."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jawa Tengah punya potensi bisnis yang luar biasa. Pastikan bisnis Anda tidak tertinggal di dunia digital."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"}]}'::jsonb,
  '{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website Development Services in Central Java: Serving Solo, Semarang, Purwokerto, and All of Central Java"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Central Java is one of Indonesia''s most economically diverse provinces. Within the same province, you will find a centuries-old batik industry in Solo and Pekalongan, the world''s largest furniture production hub in Jepara, major industrial estates in Semarang, thriving SME clusters in Kudus, world-class tourism destinations at Borobudur and the Dieng Plateau, and fast-growing cities like Purwokerto, Tegal, Magelang, and Cilacap — each with its own distinct business character."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"For all this diversity, one need is constant: "},{"type":"text","text":"a professional digital presence that can compete in today''s market.","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia Digital Solutions offers web development services across Central Java — not from a distance, but from within the province. We have offices in "},{"type":"text","text":"Semarang","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","text":"Wonosobo","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":", two strategically positioned locations that allow us to serve clients from one end of Central Java to the other."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Central Java Businesses Need a Professional Website Now"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Competition across Central Java is intensifying, and the battleground has shifted decisively online. Whether your potential customers are in the same city or across the country, they almost always begin their buying journey with a Google search."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A batik producer in Solo''s Laweyan district looking to reach buyers in Jakarta? A furniture workshop in Jepara trying to land export contracts in Europe? A food business in Purwokerto exploring franchise opportunities? A boutique hotel near Borobudur wanting to reduce reliance on Online Travel Agencies? Every one of these businesses needs a website — and a good one."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A website today is not just a digital business card. It is a sales channel, a credibility signal, and the anchor for every digital marketing effort a business undertakes."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia: Two Offices, One Commitment Across Central Java"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Our geographic presence was a deliberate choice. Our "},{"type":"text","text":"Semarang","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" office at Jl. Tanjungsari I No.18, Sumurboto, Kec. Banyumanik, Kota Semarang — the provincial capital and Central Java''s main business hub — positions us to serve clients across Greater Semarang, Kendal, Demak, and cities along the northern coastal corridor."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Our "},{"type":"text","text":"Wonosobo","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" office at Jl. Sabuk Alu RT 001/007, Wonosobo Timur, Kecamatan Wonosobo — situated in the heart of inland Central Java — serves as a service bridge for clients in Purwokerto, Banjarnegara, Kebumen, Magelang, Temanggung, and surrounding areas."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Two service points means more than geographical convenience. It means contextual understanding: we know the local business ecosystems, we understand the challenges specific to each region, and we can meet clients in person rather than conducting everything remotely."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Central Java''s Rich Business Ecosystem"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"To understand why contextual, locally-grounded "},{"type":"text","text":"web development services in Central Java","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" matter, it helps to look at the breadth of business activity across the province."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Solo and Pekalongan: Indonesia''s Batik Capitals"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Solo (Surakarta) and Pekalongan are the twin centers of Indonesia''s batik industry. Hundreds of producers — from home workshops to large-scale manufacturers — operate in both cities, serving buyers across Indonesia and internationally."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yet many batik businesses here still depend on physical markets or unstructured social media. A professional e-commerce website with well-organized product catalogs, motif and size filters, and international shipping options can fundamentally change the reach and revenue of these businesses."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jepara: Furniture for the World"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jepara is Southeast Asia''s largest furniture production center. Thousands of workshops and showrooms line its streets, exporting to Europe, the Americas, and the Middle East. For businesses at this scale, a website is not optional — it is infrastructure."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A catalog website in English, equipped with a request-for-quote system and optimized for international search, is a business asset whose value far exceeds its development cost."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kudus: Dynamic SMEs and Industry"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kudus is known for its cigarette industry and processed food businesses. Hundreds of SMEs operate here across food, beverage, and craft sectors. Many Kudus products are already recognized nationally, but lack organized digital sales channels."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"With the right website, Kudus businesses can reach new distributors, retail customers from outside the region, and overseas buyers looking for Indonesian artisanal products."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Purwokerto and Banyumas: A New Growth Center"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Purwokerto has grown rapidly as Central Java''s western education and business hub. The presence of Universitas Jenderal Soedirman (Unsoed) and several other universities has created a dynamic business ecosystem: local startups, food businesses started by students that have outgrown informal channels, training and course providers, property businesses, and more."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All of these segments need websites — from simple landing pages to more complex management systems."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tegal, Brebes, Cilacap: The Northern Coast and Southern Shore"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tegal is known for its metal and automotive industry, and for its iconic culinary exports. Brebes is Indonesia''s largest shallot-producing region. Cilacap is a key industrial city with an active port."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"In these coastal cities, digital transformation is still in early stages — meaning there is significant first-mover advantage for businesses that establish a strong online presence now."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Magelang and Borobudur: World-Class Tourism"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Borobudur Temple in Magelang attracts millions of visitors annually, including substantial numbers of international tourists. Businesses around this destination — hotels, restaurants, tour operators, souvenir shops, local artisans — have a compelling opportunity to reach international guests who research and book entirely online."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A multilingual website with integrated reservation functionality can be a decisive competitive advantage for tourism businesses in Magelang and the surrounding area."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Website Services We Offer for Central Java Businesses"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bratamedia does not build generic websites. We build digital solutions matched to the context and specific objectives of your business."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Company Profile Website"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A professional, credible representation of your business online. Ideal for firms in Semarang, Solo, or anywhere in Central Java that need a polished digital presence — law firms, consultancies, agencies, distributors, contractors, and more."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"E-Commerce Website"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"From batik sellers in Solo to furniture craftsmen in Jepara, e-commerce is a sales channel that cannot be ignored. We build functional, manageable online stores optimized for conversion."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Landing Page"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"One page, one goal: turning visitors into leads. Effective for promotional campaigns, product launches, or specific service offerings. A good starting point for businesses taking their first step into digital."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Web Portals and Web Applications"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"For more complex requirements: property agency management systems, customer portals, hotel reservation systems, or other business platforms. This is the core expertise of Bratamedia as a software house."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Our Process: From Consultation to Go-Live"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Our process always begins with listening. We do not arrive with a ready-made template and force it to fit your business. We start from scratch alongside you."}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Consultation & Requirements Analysis","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — We learn your business, your target audience, and what you want the website to achieve."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Planning & Wireframe","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Website structure is designed before any visual work begins, so all parties are aligned from the start."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"UI/UX Design","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — A look and feel that reflects your brand identity, built for usability across desktop and mobile devices."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Development","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Built with modern technology: fast, secure, and easy to manage."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Testing & Revision","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Tested across devices and browsers. You have full opportunity to give feedback."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Launch","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Your website goes live, ready to receive visitors and generate inquiries."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Post-Launch Support","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — We remain available after delivery for updates, questions, or further development."}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Beyond Central Java: Bratamedia Serves Clients Nationwide"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"While our roots are in Central Java, Bratamedia''s service reach extends across Indonesia. We have worked with clients from multiple cities nationwide, and digital projects do not have geographic boundaries."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"For businesses specifically in Wonosobo, read our article on "},{"type":"text","text":"website development services in Wonosobo","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/blog/jasa-pembuatan-website-wonosobo","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":". If you are based in Semarang, we have a dedicated guide at "},{"type":"text","text":"website development services in Semarang","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/blog/jasa-pembuatan-website-semarang","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":". For projects at a national scale, explore "},{"type":"text","text":"website development services across Indonesia","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/blog/jasa-pembuatan-website-indonesia","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can also visit our "},{"type":"text","text":"services page","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/layanan","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":" for a complete overview of our digital solutions."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Start the Conversation Today"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"If you own or manage a business in Solo, Semarang, Purwokerto, Kudus, Pekalongan, Jepara, Magelang, Tegal, Cilacap, Wonosobo — or anywhere in Central Java — and you want a website that genuinely works for your business, the Bratamedia team is ready to talk."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"You do not need a polished brief to get started. Just tell us about your business and what you want to achieve. We will guide the process from there."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Reach us through:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"WhatsApp / Phone","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": +62 851-5503-0061"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Email","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": m.iqmal.riffai@gmail.com"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Semarang Office","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Jl. Tanjungsari I No.18, Sumurboto, Kec. Banyumanik, Kota Semarang, Central Java 50269"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wonosobo Office","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Jl. Sabuk Alu RT 001/007, Wonosobo Timur, Kec. Wonosobo, Kabupaten Wonosobo, Central Java 56311"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Or visit our "},{"type":"text","text":"contact page","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"/kontak","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}]},{"type":"text","text":" and describe your project. Our team responds within 24 hours."}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"textAlign":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Central Java''s business potential is enormous. Make sure your business is positioned to capture it online."}]}]}'::jsonb,
